delivery/collection of goods associated with the non-residential uses hereby
permitted shall only be permitted to take place between the hours of 07:00 hrs
and 21:00 hrs on any day.&lt;u5:p&gt;&lt;/u5:p&gt;&lt;o:p&gt;&lt;/o:p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
